    "The development hereby approved shall be carried out in accordance with the Fire Safety Statement D12 hereby approved and thereafter maintained.\r\rReason: In the interests of Fire Safety and to ensure the safety of all building users in accordance with Policy D12 (Fire safety) of the London Plan 2021.\r",
